00:48.506 --> 00:49.507
{\an8}- AREA 50-SOMETHING.

00:49.591 --> 00:52.302
{\an8}IT'S NO SECRET
MONSTERS CALL IT HOME.

00:52.385 --> 00:56.473
{\an8}BUT THERE IS SOMETHING MORE
FRIGHTENING, MORE DANGEROUS.

00:56.556 --> 01:01.311
{\an8}INSIDE THIS SECRET OUTPOST,
THE GOVERNMENT IS HIDING...

01:01.394 --> 01:02.896
ALIENS!

01:02.979 --> 01:08.651
THAT'S RIGHT, FOLKS,
ALIENS FROM OTHER PLANETS!

01:08.735 --> 01:10.403
OF COURSE,
THE GOVERNMENT DENIES THAT,

01:10.487 --> 01:15.158
BUT THIS NEWS SCOOPER
HAS THE INSIDE SCOOP.

01:15.241 --> 01:17.869
[phone buzzing]

01:17.952 --> 01:20.580
- DEREK,
WHAT A NICE SURPRISE.

01:20.663 --> 01:23.041
- I KNOW, RIGHT?

01:23.124 --> 01:25.335
WELL, HOLD ON TO YOUR HAT,
SUSAN, BECAUSE NEWS FLASH:

01:25.418 --> 01:29.964
I'M CONSIDERING GETTING
BACK TOGETHER...WITH YOU!

01:30.048 --> 01:32.675
- UH-HUH.
- YEAH, I DECIDED YOUR BEING BIG

01:32.759 --> 01:36.346
WASN'T SO BIG AFTER ALL.
SO HOW'S ABOUT I COME OVER

01:36.429 --> 01:39.015
TO THE OLD SECRET BASE
AND WE TALK IT OUT?

01:39.098 --> 01:40.809
- OH, AND WHILE
YOU'RE HERE,

01:40.892 --> 01:42.352
MAYBE I COULD SHOW YOU
SOME THINGS,

01:42.435 --> 01:44.729
LIKE, I DON'T KNOW,
ALIENS?

01:44.813 --> 01:46.856
- ALIENS?
YEAH, THAT COULD BE COOL.

01:46.940 --> 01:48.441
- UH-HUH, NOW,
JUST ONE QUESTION, DEREK--

01:48.525 --> 01:53.238
IS IT MY TV, OR IS YOUR HAIRLINE
REALLY STARTING TO RECEDE?

01:53.321 --> 01:54.531
- WAIT.
ARE YOU WATCHING?

01:54.614 --> 01:57.492
- OH, YEAH, DEREK,
AND I'VE GOT LATE-BREAKING NEWS

01:57.575 --> 01:59.118
FOR ALL YOUR VIEWERS.
I WOULDN'T GO OUT WITH YOU

01:59.202 --> 02:01.579
IF YOU WERE
THE LAST MAN ON EARTH!

02:01.663 --> 02:02.997
[phone beep]
- CUT TO COMMERCIAL!

02:03.081 --> 02:05.625
KAREN, GET THE SHINE
OFF MY SKULL!

02:05.708 --> 02:06.960
- HA! BURN!

02:07.043 --> 02:12.006
- MY, MY, MY,
HOW INTRIGUING.

02:12.090 --> 02:15.009
- I KNOW, THEY MIXED THE PEAS
WITH THESE LITTLE ONIONS.

02:15.093 --> 02:16.719
SHOULDN'T WORK, BUT...
[chomps]

02:16.803 --> 02:19.180
BOY HOWDY, IT DOES!

02:19.264 --> 02:23.685
- I ASSURE YOU, GRAND COVERLORD,
THIS PLAN IS FLAWLESS.

02:23.768 --> 02:26.396
I WILL MAKE CONTACT
WITH THIS NEWS STOOGE.

02:26.479 --> 02:30.233
THEN WHEN WORD
OF MY EXISTENCE IS BROADCAST,

02:30.316 --> 02:32.318
THE WORLD WILL DESCEND
INTO PANIC!

02:32.402 --> 02:37.073
PLUS THE CAMERA LOVES ME.
IT'S THE CHEEKBONES.

02:41.077 --> 02:42.579
- WHERE DO YOU THINK
YOU'RE GOING?

02:42.662 --> 02:46.624
- GENERAL, I WAS JUST ABOUT TO,
YOU KNOW, HOVER AROUND.

02:46.708 --> 02:48.751
- DE-NIED!

02:48.835 --> 02:50.378
ESPECIALLY WITH A REPORTER
SNOOPING AROUND.

02:50.461 --> 02:52.422
LAST THING I NEED
IS YOUR UGLY MUG ON THE TVs.

02:52.505 --> 02:55.091
NOW, HOVER YOURSELF
BACK INTO YOUR SECURE AREA,

02:55.174 --> 02:58.845
AND GIVE ME THAT HAT!
- UM, BUT I--

02:58.928 --> 03:02.599
- ♪ DUM-DA-DUM-DA-DUM-DUM-DUM ♪

03:02.682 --> 03:06.769
AH, HERE COMES PLAN "B."
♪ DUM-DA-DUM-DA-DUM-DUM-DUM ♪

03:06.853 --> 03:10.940
- SO, BOB, QUITE A SCENE
IN THE MESS HALL TODAY, EH?

03:11.024 --> 03:12.150
- I KNOW.

03:12.233 --> 03:14.485
THOSE PEAS AND ONIONS
SHOULDN'T WORK TOGETHER,

03:14.569 --> 03:15.778
BUT GOSH DARN IT,
THEY JUST DO.

03:15.862 --> 03:18.615
- ACTUALLY, I WAS THINKING
OF ANOTHER ODD COUPLE,

03:18.698 --> 03:21.451
SUSAN AND DEREK.

03:21.534 --> 03:23.202
- THEY ARE NOT A COUPLE.

03:23.286 --> 03:25.288
SUSAN SAID SHE WOULDN'T
GO OUT WITH DEREK

03:25.371 --> 03:27.916
IF HE WAS
THE LAST MAN ON EARTH.

03:27.999 --> 03:32.045
- MM, BUT HE'S NOT
THE LAST MAN ON EARTH, IS HE?

03:32.128 --> 03:35.298
- [gasps] WHICH MEANS
SHE WOULD GO OUT WITH HIM.

03:35.381 --> 03:38.635
WOW.
MIND...BLOWN.

03:38.718 --> 03:41.346
I GOTTA GET
THOSE TWO CRAZY KIDS TOGETHER!

03:41.429 --> 03:44.933
- EXACTLY, BOB.
BRING DEREK ONTO THIS BASE.

03:45.016 --> 03:47.602
BUT TELL NO ONE
WHAT YOU'RE DOING.

03:47.685 --> 03:51.397
"THE MAN" WILL DO WHATEVER
HE CAN TO KEEP THEM APART.

03:51.481 --> 03:52.023
- "THE MAN."

03:52.106 --> 03:53.316
- YES, "THE MAN."

03:53.399 --> 03:58.154
NOW, FLY, BOB!
FLY THE ON THE WINGS OF LOVE!

04:00.740 --> 04:02.367
[phone ringing]

04:02.450 --> 04:03.910
- HELLO?
- I KNOW WHAT'S GOING ON,

04:03.993 --> 04:05.995
AND I WANT TO HELP YOU.

04:06.079 --> 04:09.499
- BOB?
- I'M ON A CALL.

04:09.582 --> 04:12.126
- WITH ME.
- WOW, HUH.

04:12.210 --> 04:13.795
HOW CRAZY IS THAT?

04:13.878 --> 04:16.923
DEREK, I'M GOING TO BRING YOU
TO YOUR ONE TRUE LOVE.

04:17.005 --> 04:20.343
- MYSELF?
- NO, SILLY, SUSAN.

04:20.426 --> 04:22.428
- YOU'RE GOING TO TAKE ME
TO SUSAN?

04:22.512 --> 04:24.013
IN THE TOP SECRET
UNDERGROUND BASE?

04:24.097 --> 04:26.975
WHERE ALL THE ALIENS ARE?
- YUP, I'M A HOPELESS ROMANTIC.

04:27.058 --> 04:28.893
[giggles]
- I'M ABOUT TO SINGLE-HANDEDLY

04:28.977 --> 04:30.603
SNEAK
INTO AREA 50-SOMETHING.

04:30.687 --> 04:33.314
I ALONE WILL FACE
THE GAUNTLET OF DEADLY--

04:33.398 --> 04:36.192
- HEY!
IT'S THIS WAY.

04:36.275 --> 04:38.569
- OKAY, BUT STAY OUT OF MY SHOT.
CAN YOU DO THAT?

04:38.653 --> 04:42.949
- [laughing]
- [grunting]

04:43.032 --> 04:45.368
OH! OH!
[grunts]

04:45.451 --> 04:48.705
- WOW, THAT WAS STINKY!

04:48.788 --> 04:50.039
- DIETL HERE.

04:50.123 --> 04:52.041
I'VE INFILTRATED
AREA 50-SOMETHING,

04:52.125 --> 04:54.502
USING METHODS
I'M NOT AT LIBERTY TO DISCLOSE.

04:54.585 --> 04:56.546
- HE CAME IN
THROUGH THE SEWER!

04:56.629 --> 04:59.424
- SO BOB,
WHEN DO WE SEE ALIENS?

04:59.507 --> 05:01.843
- ALIENS?
YOU MEAN SUSAN, RIGHT?

05:01.926 --> 05:03.720
- UH...
SLIP OF THE TONGUE?

05:03.803 --> 05:06.723
- OH, I CAN SEE THAT.
ALIENS, SUSAN.

05:06.806 --> 05:09.642
THEY'RE BOTH SPELLED
WITH...LETTERS.

05:10.935 --> 05:12.562
[gasps]
SOMEONE'S COMING.

05:12.645 --> 05:15.023
MAYBE "THE MAN."
I GOTTA HIDE YOU.

05:15.106 --> 05:16.399
- WAIT!
[shudders]

05:18.317 --> 05:20.737
- [spits]
- CALL ME CRAZY,

05:20.820 --> 05:21.779
BUT I'M NOT A FAN
OF THE LITTLE ONIONS.

05:21.863 --> 05:24.407
- HEY, GUYS!

05:24.490 --> 05:27.326
I'M NOT HIDING SUSAN'S
EX-BOYFRIEND BEHIND THIS DOOR!

05:27.410 --> 05:30.121
- YOU'RE CRAZY.
- I LIKE WHAT I LIKE.

05:30.204 --> 05:32.165
- BOB?
- I'LL GO GET SUSAN.

05:32.248 --> 05:34.751
YOU HIDE FROM "THE MAN."

05:38.129 --> 05:40.214
- THIS IS THE WORST PLACE
TO HIDE FROM "THE MAN."

05:40.298 --> 05:43.634
IT'S "THE MAN'S" OFFICE!

05:47.180 --> 05:49.932
- FINALLY,
ALONE AT LAST.

05:50.016 --> 05:52.894
- OKAY.
OKAY, "D" MAN, FOCUS NOW.

05:52.977 --> 05:54.020
GET THE SCOOP.
NETWORK GIG.

05:54.103 --> 05:57.190
EYE ON THE PRIZE.

05:57.273 --> 05:59.776
- [electronic voice] <i> KONICHIWA.</i>
TIME TO DANCING.

05:59.859 --> 06:01.778
BUSTING YOUR MOVES
ON LEVEL ONE.

06:01.861 --> 06:02.945
[dance music]

06:03.029 --> 06:05.782
- CONSIDER THEM BUSTED.

06:05.865 --> 06:07.825
♪ ♪

06:07.909 --> 06:09.952
- SURPRISE?
BOB, WHAT SURPRISE?

06:10.036 --> 06:11.204
- ALL I'M GOING TO SAY
IS WHAT YOU'RE ABOUT TO SEE

06:11.287 --> 06:15.666
WILL CHANGE YOUR LIFE,
FOREVER!

06:15.750 --> 06:17.960
- O, M, AND G.

06:18.044 --> 06:20.755
- WOW, THE GENERAL'S TOTALLY
LOOSE IN THE CABOOSE.

06:20.838 --> 06:23.716
- WHAT ARE YOU DOING?
THIS IS A PRIVATE OFFICE!

06:23.800 --> 06:25.343
GET OUT!

06:27.053 --> 06:28.888
WHERE WAS I?
OH, THAT'S RIGHT.

06:28.971 --> 06:30.807
LOCKING MY WAY
BACK TO FUNKY TOWN.

06:30.890 --> 06:33.559
♪ ♪

06:33.643 --> 06:37.021
- WELL, BOB, THAT DID
CHANGE MY LIFE...FOREVER.

06:37.105 --> 06:38.147
NOT FOR THE BETTER.

06:38.231 --> 06:41.275
- AH, BOB!
HAVE YOU FOUND THE REPORT--

06:41.359 --> 06:44.862
[muffled speech]
- "THE MAN" HAS EARS EVERYWHERE.

06:45.404 --> 06:49.534
- [humming]

06:49.617 --> 06:50.827
- THERE YOU ARE!

06:50.910 --> 06:52.703
COME ON, I'M TAKING YOU
STRAIGHT TO SUSAN.

06:52.787 --> 06:57.333
- BOB, WAIT, YOU KNOW, I LIKE
THE HIDING/SURPRISE THING.

06:57.416 --> 07:00.002
BUT MAYBE WE NEED
TO HIDE ME SOMEWHERE

07:00.086 --> 07:03.131
A LITTLE MORE SECRET
AND SECURE.

07:03.214 --> 07:06.300
- WHAT'D YOU HAVE IN MIND,
YOU SLY DOG?

07:06.384 --> 07:08.177
[barks and laughs]

07:08.261 --> 07:11.681
- WELL, DO YOU HAVE ANY,
I DON'T KNOW,

07:11.764 --> 07:15.017
ALIENS ON THIS BASE?

07:15.101 --> 07:17.895
- GENIUS!
NOBODY BUT NOBODY GOES IN HERE,

07:17.979 --> 07:20.356
EVER!
IT'S PERFECT.

07:20.439 --> 07:23.401
- [laughs] PERFECT.

07:23.484 --> 07:26.571
WAIT, WHAT'S
WITH THE GIANT DOGGY TOYS?

07:26.654 --> 07:27.864
- [growling]

07:27.947 --> 07:28.698
- UNLESS SOMEBODY'S
GOT A GIANT--

07:28.781 --> 07:30.950
- [roars]
- [screams]

07:31.033 --> 07:34.203
- AND YOU'RE SURE THIS ISN'T
ANOTHER MONGER BOOTY QUAKE,

07:34.287 --> 07:35.371
RIGHT?
- OH, NO,

07:35.454 --> 07:37.874
YOU'RE GOING TO WANT
TO SEE THIS.

07:38.875 --> 07:41.002
TA-DA!

07:41.085 --> 07:43.880
- [licking]

07:43.963 --> 07:47.383
- OKAY, BOB, THANKS...
FOR SHOWING ME...THAT.

07:47.466 --> 07:48.968
- [licking]

07:49.051 --> 07:50.052
[hiccups]

07:50.136 --> 07:51.929
- [screams]

07:52.013 --> 07:53.264
[shudders]

07:53.347 --> 07:54.557
- [burps]

07:54.640 --> 07:56.893
- THAT THING ATE ME.
I WAS EATEN.

07:56.976 --> 07:59.437
[sobbing]
I DON'T WANT TO BE EATEN.

07:59.520 --> 08:01.606
WAIT, DID IT DIGEST
ANY OF MY HAIR?

08:01.689 --> 08:05.026
- UH, MAYBE.
WAS THIS SHINY SPOT ALWAYS HERE?

08:05.109 --> 08:07.820
- HAIR DAMAGE!
NO SCOOP IS WORTH THAT.

08:07.904 --> 08:09.155
UNLESS IT GETS ME
MY OWN SHOW.

08:09.238 --> 08:10.615
HO, HO, THEN I COULD--

08:10.698 --> 08:12.450
NO, NO, "D" MAN,
THAT'S CRAZY TALK!

08:12.533 --> 08:15.036
YOU CAN'T REPLACE
HAIR LIKE MINE.

08:15.119 --> 08:18.247
THE CURL.
I CAN'T PAY THAT PRICE.

08:18.331 --> 08:20.583
THIS STORY
IS JUST NOT WORTH IT!

08:20.666 --> 08:22.919
- NO, DEREK!
I WILL NOT HAVE YOU

08:23.002 --> 08:27.506
GIVING UP ON THIS STORY,
THIS FAIRY TALE, THIS ROMANCE.

08:27.590 --> 08:29.759
YOU KNOW WHAT?
YOU NEED A PEP TALK,

08:29.842 --> 08:32.510
FROM MY PEPPY FRIEND.
[chuckles]

08:32.595 --> 08:34.847
- [electronic voice]
BUSTING YOUR MOVES ON LEVEL ONE.

08:34.931 --> 08:38.226
- LEVEL ONE CAN PREPARE
TO BE ANNIHILATED

08:38.308 --> 08:40.937
BY MY "SKILLZ"...
WITH A "Z."

08:41.020 --> 08:42.188
- COVERTON!

08:42.270 --> 08:47.944
- AH, BOB AND THE...
TV BLABBER-PERSON OF ILL REPUTE.

08:48.027 --> 08:50.154
- SO YOU HAVE SEEN
MY SHOW?

08:50.238 --> 08:52.156
- INDEED.
I FIND YOUR APPETITE

08:52.240 --> 08:54.659
FOR THE EXPLOITATION
AND DEBASEMENT OF OTHERS

08:54.742 --> 08:56.327
POSITIVELY DELIGHTFUL.

08:56.410 --> 08:57.662
- OH.
UH, COOL.

08:57.745 --> 09:00.790
- COVERTON, CAN I LEAVE DEREK
HERE WITH YOU?

09:00.873 --> 09:03.417
HE NEEDS A PEP TALK
SOMETHING FIERCE.

09:03.501 --> 09:07.630
- DEAREST DEREK,
LET US CHAT.

09:07.713 --> 09:10.633
- GREAT, YOU TWO CHEW THE FAT.
[singsong] I'LL GET SUSAN.

09:12.635 --> 09:13.219
[camera snaps]

09:13.302 --> 09:16.055
- GET ME IN 3/4 PROFILE

09:16.138 --> 09:18.516
AND MAKE SURE THE LIGHTING
ISN'T TOO HARSH.

09:18.599 --> 09:21.018
SOMETIMES THERE'S AN AWFUL,
UNFLATTERING SHINE

09:21.102 --> 09:22.645
ON MY FOREHEAD.

09:22.728 --> 09:25.564
- MR. ALIEN, WE SPEAK
EACH OTHER'S LANGUAGE.

09:28.067 --> 09:30.611
- NO REALLY, SUSAN.
THIS TIME FOR SURE.

09:30.695 --> 09:32.613
- OKAY, BUT THIS IS
THE LAST TIME.

09:32.697 --> 09:36.826
- SUSAN, BOB,
WHAT CAN I DO FOR YOU?

09:36.909 --> 09:39.662
- WHERE'S DEREK?
- WAIT, DEREK WAS HERE?

09:39.745 --> 09:43.082
- AH, DANG!
I RUINED THE SURPRISE.

09:43.165 --> 09:45.001
- DEREK'S LONG GONE NOW.

09:45.084 --> 09:46.294
BUT HE DID WALK AWAY
WITH A HOT EXCLUSIVE:

09:46.377 --> 09:49.714
"CLOSE ENCOUNTER: ME!"

09:49.797 --> 09:52.008
THE WORLD'S GOING TO LOVE IT.
[evil laugh]

09:52.091 --> 09:54.844
- OH, NO!

09:54.927 --> 09:57.722
[beeps]
- AH, NO SIGNAL.

09:57.805 --> 09:59.515
WHY DO THEY HAVE TO PUT
THESE SECRET INSTALLATIONS

09:59.598 --> 10:01.267
IN THE MIDDLE OF NOWHERE?
- YEAH,

10:01.350 --> 10:03.936
SO YOU CAN'T UPLOAD PICTURES
OR VIDEOS.

10:04.020 --> 10:05.730
- SUSAN?
IS THAT...YOU?

10:05.813 --> 10:07.982
YOU'RE--YOU'RE NORMAL!
- NORMAL?

10:08.065 --> 10:11.527
- YEAH, YOU'RE NOT A 50-FOOT
GIANT ABOMINATION ANYMORE.

10:11.610 --> 10:14.238
WHY DIDN'T YOU TELL ME,
BABY?

10:14.322 --> 10:16.866
NOW WE CAN TOTALLY
GET BACK TOGETHER.

10:16.949 --> 10:18.034
FOR REALS.

10:18.117 --> 10:19.368
MIGHT FIX THE HAIR,
THOUGH.

10:19.452 --> 10:22.330
BUT OTHER THAN THAT,
YOU'RE TOTALLY NORMAL AGAIN.

10:22.413 --> 10:24.165
SWEET.
- DEREK,

10:24.248 --> 10:27.918
I'VE ALWAYS BEEN NORMAL,
EVEN WHEN I'M GINORMOUS.

10:28.002 --> 10:29.378
- [screams]

10:29.462 --> 10:31.797
- I WANT YOU TO MEET SQWEEP.
YOU'LL LIKE SQWEEP.

10:31.881 --> 10:33.716
SQWEEP'S AN ALIEN.
- REALLY? AN ALIEN?

10:33.799 --> 10:38.346
- YEAH, AN ALIEN WITH A NICE
LITTLE MEMORY WIPER.

10:38.429 --> 10:41.849
- WAIT! NO!
NOOOOO!

10:41.932 --> 10:46.020
- AH, LOOK AT THEM.
DEREK AND SUSAN TOGETHER AGAIN,

10:46.103 --> 10:48.606
JUST LIKE PEAS AND ONIONS.
[laughs]

10:51.817 --> 10:54.695
- [gasps]
WHERE AM I?

10:54.779 --> 10:58.574
WAIT A SECOND.
WHO AM I?

10:58.657 --> 11:02.161
"YOUR NAME IS DEREK DI-ET-L,

11:02.244 --> 11:05.498
"AND YOU HAVE NO CHANCE
WITH SUSAN MURPHY.

11:05.581 --> 11:08.250
P.S. YOUR HAIRLINE
IS DEFINITELY RECEDING."

11:08.334 --> 11:10.044
[screams]

11:11.337 --> 11:15.091
[sci-fi movie music]

11:15.174 --> 11:20.679
♪ ♪

11:22.056 --> 11:24.892
{\an8}- IT'S FINALLY HERE, BOYS.
TODAY'S THE DAY!

11:24.975 --> 11:25.893
{\an8}[all cheering]

11:28.646 --> 11:31.190
{\an8}YOU HAVE NO IDEA WHAT TODAY
IS THE DAY OF...DO YOU?

11:31.273 --> 11:32.233
{\an8}- NOT A CLUE.
- NOT REALLY, NO.

11:32.316 --> 11:33.692
- JANUARY 43RD!

11:33.776 --> 11:35.277
[all cheering]

11:35.361 --> 11:36.946
- TODAY'S THE DAY MONGER IS
GOING OFF BASE FOR THE WEEKEND,

11:37.029 --> 11:40.616
WHICH MEANS HE'LL BE
PUTTING SOMEONE IN CHARGE

11:40.699 --> 11:41.742
WHILE HE'S AWAY.
GET READY, GUYS.

11:41.826 --> 11:44.453
TODAY IS SUSAN MURPHY'S
TIME TO SHINE!

11:44.537 --> 11:46.163
- YEAH!
- ALL RIGHT!

11:46.247 --> 11:47.957
- I OBJECT!

11:48.040 --> 11:52.420
THE GIANTESS CAN BARELY CONTROL
HER OWN MONSTERS.

11:52.503 --> 11:54.964
IF ANYONE IS TO BE LEFT
IN COMMAND, IT SHOULD BE ME.

11:55.047 --> 11:56.507
- PBBBT.

11:56.590 --> 11:58.801
- YOU KNOW,
ON MY PLANET,

11:58.884 --> 12:02.471
THIS IS AN EXTREMELY
INSULTING GESTURE!

12:02.555 --> 12:04.098
- ENOUGH!
COVERTON,

12:04.181 --> 12:05.182
I'VE ALREADY
MADE UP MY MIND.

12:05.266 --> 12:07.476
THE ONE I'M LEAVING
IN CHARGE IS--

12:07.560 --> 12:12.940
- STA-A-A-ABI!
- NO-O-O-O.

12:13.023 --> 12:14.817
THE RULE-BOT 9000.

12:14.900 --> 12:16.569
- WHAT THE WHAT?

12:16.652 --> 12:18.362
- WHAT IS THIS RULE-BOT?

12:18.446 --> 12:20.781
- FASCINATING.

12:20.865 --> 12:23.659
IT APPEARS TO BE SOME SORT
OF PREHISTORIC COMPUTING DEVICE.

12:23.742 --> 12:26.203
- [grunts and sniffs]

12:26.287 --> 12:28.330
[roars]

12:28.414 --> 12:31.208
- [muffled yelling]

12:31.292 --> 12:34.211
- THE RULE-BOT AIN'T
JUST ANY COMP-U-BOX.

12:34.295 --> 12:35.838
I HAD IT BUILT
BACK IN THE COLD WAR

12:35.921 --> 12:37.673
TO ASSUME COMMAND
IN CASE OF CATASTROPHIC

12:37.756 --> 12:39.800
WORLD-ENDING EVENTS.
- PARADOX!

12:39.884 --> 12:43.179
IF THE WORLD ENDED, WHO WOULD BE
ALIVE FOR IT TO COMMAND?

12:43.262 --> 12:45.055
- NOSY-BODIES LIKE YOU
WHO ASK TOO MANY QUESTIONS!

12:45.139 --> 12:48.350
NOW, CLAM UP!
THE RULE-BOT'S BEEN PROGRAMMED

12:48.434 --> 12:51.020
TO ENFORCE EVERY RULE
AND REGULATION IN THE BOOK.

12:51.103 --> 12:52.438
OBSERVE.

12:52.521 --> 12:53.939
[electronic humming]

12:54.023 --> 12:57.902
- [electronic voice]
RULE VIOLATION 34-B, LITTERBUG!

12:57.985 --> 12:59.653
- [laughing]
HOT DOG ALMIGHTY!

12:59.737 --> 13:02.198
THAT WAS BLEEDING TECH
BACK IN THE DAY,

13:02.281 --> 13:04.033
AND I CAN'T THINK
OF A BETTER PERSON

13:04.116 --> 13:05.117
TO LEAVE IN CHARGE.

13:05.201 --> 13:07.578
- BUT IT'S NOT EVEN
A PERSON.

13:07.661 --> 13:08.829
- AT EASE, SOLDIERS.

13:08.913 --> 13:11.165
DON'T BURN THE BASE DOWN
WHILE I'M AWAY!

13:11.248 --> 13:12.541
- [growling]
- UGH!

13:12.625 --> 13:13.584
- LOOK ON THE BRIGHT SIDE,
SUZE.

13:13.667 --> 13:15.211
THIS THING CAN'T POSSIBLY
BE WORSE

13:15.294 --> 13:18.464
THAN IF COVERTON WAS IN CHARGE.
SO THERE'S THAT, RIGHT?

13:19.965 --> 13:23.886
- RULE VIOLATION 16-D.
UNSANITARY CONSUMPTION.

13:27.223 --> 13:30.559
RULE VIOLATION 22-G.
BUCK NAKED IN PUBLIC AREA.

13:30.643 --> 13:34.396
- AH!
MY SKIVVIES!

13:34.480 --> 13:36.524
- RULE VIOLATION 49-C.
- AH!

13:36.607 --> 13:38.442
- MIXING
HAZARDOUS CHEMICALS.

13:38.526 --> 13:40.194
- [grunts]
- HELMETS MUST BE WORN

13:40.277 --> 13:42.488
DURING COMBAT DRILLS.

13:42.571 --> 13:45.908
- VIOLATION! UNACCOMPANIED MINOR
WITHOUT HALL PASS.

13:45.991 --> 13:48.244
- RULE VIOLATION.
RULE VIOLATION!

13:48.327 --> 13:49.495
RULE VIOLATION!
- MAKE IT STOP!

13:49.578 --> 13:53.624
- OBEY OR FACE PUNISHMENT!

13:53.707 --> 13:55.751
- MOVE IT, PEOPLE.
WE'VE GOT A RULE BOX TO WHOMP.

13:55.834 --> 13:58.087
- GUYS,
IT'S NOT THAT BAD.

13:58.170 --> 13:59.838
- IT'S GONE RULE-MAD,
SUSAN.

13:59.922 --> 14:02.174
MONTHS OF CARELESS
EXPERIMENT PLANNING,

14:02.258 --> 14:04.593
AND BOOM!
GONE!

14:04.677 --> 14:08.097
I MEANT CAREFUL PLANNING,
OF COURSE.

14:08.180 --> 14:10.432
- YEAH, AND EVER SINCE
I STARTED WEARING CLOTHES,

14:10.516 --> 14:13.269
I HAVE TO USE MY OTHER SENSES
TO SEE WHO I'M TALKING TO,

14:13.352 --> 14:15.938
LIKE TASTE.
[licking]

14:16.021 --> 14:17.773
- I GET ENFORCING
NORMAL RULES,

14:17.856 --> 14:20.025
BUT THIS THING'S JUST
A POWER-MAD NITPICKER.

14:20.109 --> 14:21.277
- AGREED.

14:21.360 --> 14:23.070
- ANNOYING NOISE MACHINE

14:23.153 --> 14:26.240
WILL NOT LET STA'ABI
MAKE COMBAT.

14:26.323 --> 14:28.075
- I DON'T EVEN KNOW WHAT
A HALL PASS IS.

14:28.158 --> 14:31.328
- YES AND IT SCOLDED ME
FOR PLANNING AN INVASION!

14:32.705 --> 14:33.872
OF PRIVACY.

14:33.956 --> 14:37.710
LOVE THOSE CELEBRITY
GOSSIP SITES.

14:37.793 --> 14:40.671
- [licking]
WHO'S THERE?

14:40.754 --> 14:43.424
- RULE VIOLATION 54-C.
NO LICKING.

14:43.507 --> 14:45.718
- OKAY.
WHAT'S THE DEAL, MAN?

14:45.801 --> 14:48.220
WHY ARE YOU BUSTING OUR CHOPS
FOR RULES THAT DON'T MATTER?

14:48.304 --> 14:49.680
- RULE-BOT
DOES NOT COMPUTE.

14:49.763 --> 14:52.433
- OKAY, THAT'S RETRO, BUT--
- ALL RULES MATTER.

14:52.516 --> 14:55.978
OBEY RULES OR YOU WILL
FACE PUNISHMENT.

14:56.061 --> 14:58.147
- IT'S SCIENTIFICALLY IMPOSSIBLE
TO OBEY ALL YOUR RULES.

14:58.230 --> 15:01.650
- SUBJECT SUSAN HAS NOT YET
COMMITTED A SINGLE VIOLATION.

15:01.734 --> 15:04.278
- WHAT?
I'M A GOOD GIRL.

15:04.361 --> 15:05.863
- [taunting]
TEACHER'S PET.

15:05.946 --> 15:07.489
- [taunting humming]

15:07.573 --> 15:08.741
- [gasps]

15:08.824 --> 15:10.492
[grumbling]

15:10.576 --> 15:12.786
- LOOK, MONGER PUT
THE RULE-BOT IN CHARGE.

15:12.870 --> 15:16.165
IT'S ONLY FOR ONE WEEKEND,
SO LET'S JUST DEAL, 'KAY?

15:16.248 --> 15:18.250
- OH, WE GONNA DEAL.

15:18.334 --> 15:21.045
- VIOLATORS...
EVERYWHERE.

15:21.128 --> 15:25.132
- THERE, THAT MUST BE
THE MANUAL SHUTDOWN.

15:25.215 --> 15:26.508
- ALL RIGHT NOW,
FOCUS.

15:26.592 --> 15:28.761
THIS IS FOR REALS,
NOT FOR PLAYS.

15:28.844 --> 15:30.804
WE GOTTA BE STEALTHY,
LIKE THE NIGHT.

15:30.888 --> 15:33.849
[dramatic music]

15:33.932 --> 15:40.939
♪ ♪

15:47.196 --> 15:49.239
[flushing]

15:55.287 --> 15:57.081
[robot powering down]

15:57.164 --> 15:58.624
- YEAH!
- ALL RIGHT!

15:58.707 --> 16:01.210
- WHO'S YOUR MONSTERS?
WE YOUR MONSTERS!

16:01.293 --> 16:02.878
- CPU CHECKMATE!

16:02.961 --> 16:04.546
- SLO-MO VICTORY FIVE?
DA-DA-DA-DA-DA-DA-DA.

16:04.630 --> 16:05.923
DA-DA-DA-DA-DA-DA-DA.

16:06.006 --> 16:08.634
STILL NOT THERE.
DA-DA-DA-DA-DA-DA-DA.

16:08.717 --> 16:10.511
YEAH.

16:10.594 --> 16:12.971
SO GUESSING THAT BUTTON
JUST RESETS IT, HUH?

16:13.055 --> 16:16.475
- I'M SORRY, WHAT?
- RULE VIOLATORS!

16:16.558 --> 16:18.352
VIOLATORS
WILL BE PUNISHED!

16:18.435 --> 16:20.229
- HE DID IT!
- IT WAS HIS IDEA!

16:20.312 --> 16:21.814
[grunting]
- VIOLATORS!

16:21.897 --> 16:24.566
- SUSAN, IT'S BEING MEAN!
MAKE IT STOP!

16:24.650 --> 16:26.443
- UM...
OKAY, UH...

16:26.527 --> 16:31.240
MR. BOT, LINK AND COCKROACH
ARE SORRY FOR WHATEVER THEY DID.

16:31.323 --> 16:32.574
AND IF YOU
LEAVE THEM ALONE,

16:32.658 --> 16:33.826
I PROMISE TO MAKE SURE
THEY BEHAVE FROM NOW ON.

16:33.909 --> 16:35.703
YOU CAN TRUST ME.
LIKE YOU SAID,

16:35.786 --> 16:38.914
I HAVEN'T BROKEN ANY RULES.

16:38.997 --> 16:43.168
- UNTIED SHOES ARE A VIOLATION
OF DRESS CODE 37-A!

16:43.252 --> 16:44.753
RULE BREAKER!

16:44.837 --> 16:46.213
- OKAY,
IT'S JUST BEING MEAN.

16:46.296 --> 16:49.591
- YOU WILL OBEY ALL RULES
OR YOU WILL BE PUNISHED!

16:49.675 --> 16:51.593
- PUNISHED?
HOW EXACTLY?

16:51.677 --> 16:54.471
- UM...
WITH PUNISHMENT!

16:54.555 --> 16:56.682
- YEAH, BUT SPECIFICALLY,
HOW?

16:56.765 --> 17:01.395
- YOU DARE QUESTION RULE-BOT?
YOU WILL GET DOUBLE PUNISHMENT!

17:01.478 --> 17:02.521
- OH, I DARE.

17:02.604 --> 17:03.272
COME ON WITH THE DETAILS
ALREADY.

17:03.355 --> 17:06.023
- T-T-T-TRIPLE PUNISHMENT!

17:06.108 --> 17:09.111
THERE, RULE-BOT HAS DECIDED
AND WILL LEAVE NOW.

17:09.194 --> 17:12.364
- WAIT, YOU CAN'T REALLY
PUNISH US AT ALL, CAN YOU?

17:12.448 --> 17:13.281
- SAY WHAT?

17:13.365 --> 17:15.534
- NO, RULE-BOT
CAN PUNISH.

17:15.617 --> 17:16.993
RULE-BOT JUST DOESN'T
FEEL LIKE IT RIGHT NOW.

17:17.077 --> 17:19.788
- WAIT, SO LET ME
GET THIS STRAIGHT.

17:19.872 --> 17:21.707
ALL THIS THING CAN DO
IS YELL AT US?

17:21.790 --> 17:23.625
- HAS IT BEEN DOING
ANYTHING ELSE?

17:23.709 --> 17:26.002
- WELL, THAT KINDA
CHANGES THINGS.

17:26.086 --> 17:27.296
[dance music]

17:27.378 --> 17:28.881
- [growls]

17:28.964 --> 17:32.050
♪ ♪

17:32.134 --> 17:35.137
- HA!
VICTORY BELONGS TO STA'ABI!

17:35.220 --> 17:36.346
- [roars]

17:36.430 --> 17:39.016
- [grunting]

17:39.099 --> 17:41.143
- [humming]

17:41.226 --> 17:44.354
- NO HORSEPLAY IN WORK AREAS.
ILLEGAL POP AND LOCKING.

17:44.438 --> 17:46.899
- OH, STOP BEING
SUCH A FUDDY-DUDDY.

17:46.982 --> 17:49.318
- RULE-BOT HAS LEARNED
HUMILIATION.

17:49.401 --> 17:52.237
- LINK, YOU MIGHT BE
PUSHING THIS A BIT.

17:52.321 --> 17:54.656
YOU DON'T EVEN SEE COVERTON
GOOFING OFF THIS MUCH.

17:57.117 --> 17:59.703
- THIS IS
MY CONQUERING DANCE.

17:59.787 --> 18:02.331
MM.
[humming]

18:02.414 --> 18:03.832
OH! OH!

18:03.916 --> 18:05.626
INFERNAL GRAVITY!
[snaps fingers]

18:05.709 --> 18:09.129
[struggling]

18:09.213 --> 18:11.256
♪ ♪

18:11.340 --> 18:13.842
- PUSHING IT.
- CHILL, SUZE.

18:13.926 --> 18:16.053
WE'LL SPEED-CLEAN
BEFORE MONGER GETS HOME.

18:23.268 --> 18:26.188
BESIDES, IT'S NOT LIKE
THAT RULE BOX

18:26.271 --> 18:28.190
CAN TAKE ITSELF
OUT OF THE WALL OR ANYTHING.

18:28.273 --> 18:29.650
[metal bending]

18:32.152 --> 18:33.070
[all gasp]

18:33.153 --> 18:34.071
both: HUH?

18:34.154 --> 18:35.030
- [gasps]

18:35.114 --> 18:38.909
RULE-BOT IS UPGRADED!

18:40.911 --> 18:43.080
- [grunts]
- LOOK OUT!

18:43.163 --> 18:44.623
[both grunt]

18:44.706 --> 18:45.833
- AH!

18:47.125 --> 18:48.794
- A FORCE FIELD?

18:48.877 --> 18:50.921
I DIDN'T KNOW
I HAD ONE OF THOSE.

18:51.004 --> 18:53.048
- RULE BREAKER!

18:53.131 --> 18:56.635
- THAT'S AN EPSILON CLASS
RUMP MASSAGER.

18:56.718 --> 18:59.346
IT CAN'T POSS--
[babbles]

19:01.306 --> 19:02.140
[babbling]

19:02.224 --> 19:04.935
- TIME TO GO! UGH!
- [grunts]

19:05.018 --> 19:08.730
- WHO RULES THE RULE-BOT?
NO ONE!

19:08.814 --> 19:10.941
RULE-BOT RULES ALL!

19:11.024 --> 19:13.819
MOO-HOO-HAH HAH HAH HAH!

19:16.280 --> 19:18.198
- OKAY, I'VE GOT A PLAN
TO SAVE MY TEAM,

19:18.282 --> 19:19.449
BUT I'LL NEED YOUR HELP.
- [straining]

19:19.533 --> 19:21.702
OH, GOODY.
I HEART MONSTERS.

19:21.785 --> 19:22.911
HOPE AGAIN.

19:22.995 --> 19:25.414
- YOU KNOW, MAYBE YOU'RE RIGHT.

19:25.497 --> 19:26.999
I DOUBT EVEN A MIND
AS BRILLIANT AS YOURS

19:27.082 --> 19:29.251
COULD DEFEAT THE RULE-BOT.

19:29.334 --> 19:33.714
- OH, DO YOU HONESTLY THINK
REVERSE PSYCHOLOGY

19:33.797 --> 19:35.591
WILL WORK
ON AN ALIEN MIND?

19:35.674 --> 19:37.634
- AN ALIEN THAT CAN'T
OUTTHINK A ROBOT.

19:37.718 --> 19:41.805
- YES, I CAN!
I CAN AND I WILL SHOW YOU!

19:41.889 --> 19:43.932
COME,
INSIGNIFICANT HUMAN.

19:44.016 --> 19:47.769
I SHALL LEAD US
TO GLORY AND VICTORY!

19:47.853 --> 19:49.897
[ripping]
[screams]

19:49.980 --> 19:52.858
THAT TOOK THE HAIRS!
ALL THE HAIRS!

19:54.234 --> 19:55.193
- NOW, TELL RULE-BOT.

19:55.277 --> 19:58.447
WHAT PUNISHMENT OPTIONS
DO YOU PREFER?

19:58.530 --> 20:03.785
"A," LASER PUNISHMENT?
"B," BAZOOKA PUNISHMENT?

20:03.869 --> 20:06.288
- OR "C,"
RULE-BOT PUNISHMENT.

20:06.371 --> 20:08.832
- ARCHAIC BOT,
YOU HAVE CHALLENGED

20:08.916 --> 20:13.170
EARTH'S GREATEST COVERTON
TO COMBAT.

20:13.253 --> 20:16.757
NOW, FEAST UPON THE DOOM
OF YOUR MISTAKE!

20:16.840 --> 20:18.759
OH!
[whimpers]

20:18.842 --> 20:21.428
- [evil laugh]
RULE-BOT'S TURN TO PUNISH!

20:23.680 --> 20:27.476
- [whimpering]

20:27.559 --> 20:30.437
CHANGE OF PLANS!
EVERYONE FOR THEMSELVES!

20:30.520 --> 20:34.566
[whimpering]

20:34.650 --> 20:35.609
[babbling yell]

20:35.692 --> 20:37.569
AH!

20:37.653 --> 20:39.029
[crash]
UGH!

20:39.112 --> 20:42.491
- HA HA HA!
RULE-BOT LAUGHS AT YOU.

20:42.574 --> 20:46.161
DID YOU REALLY THINK AN ALIEN
COULD OUTTHINK A COMPUTER?

20:46.244 --> 20:49.289
- MM, NOPE.
THAT WAS JUST MY DISTRACTION.

20:49.373 --> 20:51.792
YOUR SHOES ARE UNTIED.

20:52.918 --> 20:54.962
[warning beeps]
WHICH MEANS

20:55.045 --> 20:56.838
YOU JUST BROKE A RULE!

20:56.922 --> 21:00.092
- NO! NO!
ILLOGICAL!

21:00.175 --> 21:02.844
RULE-BOT CANNOT BREAK...

21:02.928 --> 21:05.681
[prolonged yell]
RU-U-ULES!

21:05.764 --> 21:08.517
OH.

21:13.563 --> 21:14.564
[all grunt]

21:14.648 --> 21:16.441
- YOU GUYS ALL RIGHT?
- HUZZAH, SUSAN!

21:16.525 --> 21:18.193
BRILLIANT PLAN!
- RETRO.

21:18.276 --> 21:19.945
- YAY!
- SUZE,

21:20.028 --> 21:22.155
YOU MAY NOT BE MONGER'S CHOICE
FOR SUBSTITUTE LEADER,

21:22.239 --> 21:25.158
BUT AS FAR AS TEAM MONSTER GOES,
YOU'LL ALWAYS BE OURS.

21:25.242 --> 21:26.284
- THANKS, GUYS.
- OH, PLEASE,

21:26.368 --> 21:30.205
I LED THE ATTACK.
THIS IS MY DOING!

21:30.288 --> 21:32.332
COVERTON DID THIS!

21:33.291 --> 21:35.127
- YOU DESTROYED
MY RULE-BOT?

21:35.210 --> 21:38.296
- GENERAL? NO!
[stutters]

21:38.380 --> 21:39.798
IT'S NOT WHAT IT SEEMS,
YOU KNOW.

21:39.881 --> 21:41.091
I-I-I CAN FI--

21:42.092 --> 21:43.969
UGH!

21:44.970 --> 21:45.971
[chuckles]
